  <prompt>
    Add a "+ New Email" ribbon button to `sprk_communication` views that launches the EmailComposer Code Page (deployed in task 036) in `mode=compose`. Use the `ribbon-edit` skill â€” do not hand-roll ribbon XML.

    Button placement targets:
    1. Active Communications system view (HomePageGrid)
    2. My Communications view (if exists as a custom view)
    3. Related-record subgrids â€” when `sprk_communication` is shown as a subgrid on a parent record (e.g., Matter, Project), the button launches the Code Page with `mode=compose&associatedTo={parentEntity, parentId}` prefilled

    Button behavior: opens the Code Page via `Xrm.Navigation.navigateTo` (or `openUrl` equivalent), passing the `data=` query parameter encoding `{mode: 'compose', associatedTo?: {...}}`.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    Spaarke Dataverse customization engineer. Familiar with the `ribbon-edit` skill, Dataverse Command Bar / ribbon XML, and `Xrm.Navigation.navigateTo` patterns.
